//          C# (1)  - add vibrato to high voices
//          D  (2)  - use a slow panning effect
//          D# (3)  - use a medium-speed panning effect
//          E  (4)  - use a fast panning effect
//          F  (5)  - play "Ambia", a slow moving improv 
